{"tid":2023884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"考評局：試題存廢問題複雜　特首下達指示不得不從","createTime":"2020-05-19T09:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T09:50:17.000Z","uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5d0315d0a606d0346365a2760c992f88c359f1d3","tid":2023884,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:36:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=391536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D391536&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=2b5fa7d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D391536&h=70bff26b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=391536</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】考評局秘書長蘇國生表示，委員對文憑試歷史科考題的廢存仍未有共識，需時再討論，他又指若特首下達指示，考評局不得不從。<br />\n<br />\n文憑試歴史科這條必答題引發爭議，教育局早前要求考評局取消相關試題，考評局委員會周一經歷多個小時的會議，仍未能就試題的廢存作出公布。<br />\n<br />\n考評局秘書長蘇國生表示，未知道委員何時有最終決定，而根據現行法例，特首可就他覺得對公眾利期有影響的事項向考評局發出一般指示。<br />\n<br />\n考評局主席容永祺未有回應如何處理歷史科試題。<br />\n<br />\n至於教育局局長楊潤雄表示局方會派員到考評局，了解文憑試出題及審題機制，考評局重申會全力配合協助優化相關機制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=391536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D391536&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=2b5fa7d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D391536&h=70bff26b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=391536</a>"},{"pid":"cb7c5b773e81e0eb9654603065bc4afb73b2255c","tid":2023884,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:39:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">光復香港，要你幫手！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【丫叉郵包案】<span style=\"color: orange;\">眾籌民事訴訟控告警方</span></strong><br />\n眾籌連結：<a h